headline.main: North Carolina's Justin Jackson Leads AP All-ACC Team
headline.print_headline: North Carolina's Justin Jackson Leads AP All-ACC Team

lead_paragraph: North Carolina forward Justin Jackson is The Associated Press player of the year in the Atlantic Coast Conference and Georgia Tech's Josh Pastner is its coach of the year.
